project: DO YOU REALLY WANT TO DELETE THE SAVED DATA?
- TOP-LEFT BUTTONS: TRAIN MELEE, RANGED, AND SUPER UNITS.
- TOP-RIGHT BUTTONS: SPECIAL ABILITY, ADVANCE AGE, AND FUNDS.
- SELECT YOUR BASE (LEFT-SIDE BUILDING) TO BUILD OR SELL TURRETS AND INCREASE TURRET SLOTS.
- HEALTH BARS ARE DISPLAYED AT THE TOP OF THE SCREEN.
- YOU MUST DESTROY THE BASE OF YOUR OPPONENT BY TRAINING UNITS AND ATTACKING IT. DEFEAT ALL 5 LEVELS TO BEAT THE GAME.
- PAN THE SCREEN TO SEE THE WHOLE ARENA.
Through your leadership, the scarab civilization has battled across the ages and emerged victorious!
